OKLAHOMA RAILWAY COMPANY, Debtor, Robert K. Johnston and A. C. DeBolt, Trustees, v. MISSISSIPPI VALLEY TRUST COMPANY, Claimant and Trustee. No. 3274. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit Feb. 12, 1946. Richardson, Shartel, Cochran- & Pruet, of Oklahoma City, Okl., for appellant. Keaton, Wells & Johnston, of Oklahoma City, Old., for appellee.

Before PHILLIPS, Circuit Judge, and SYMES, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Cross-appeal dismissed on motion of cross-appellant.
